headline: Is Tesla's Rising Capital Spending Putting Strain on Cash Flows?
summary: TSLA's free cash flow plunges as capital spending climbs, with revenues falling and investments in projects yet to pay off.

headline: BizClik Brings Global Leaders Together at Sustainability LIVE: Climate Week NYC 2025
summary: NEW YORK - 19 September - BizClik, the global B2B media and events company, has announced the upcoming Sustainability LIVE: Climate Week NYC 2025, taking place on 22 September 2025 at Convene, 360 Madison Avenue, New York City. Building on the success of the Sustainability LIVE global event series, this one-day forum will unite more than 500 senior executives from across business, technology, procurement, and policy to accelerate climate action and shape strategies for a sustainable future. headline: This Dividend Stock Is Up 10% This Year and Amazon Could Take It Even Higher
summary: General Motors’ stock is up 10% this year and could climb further as Amazon’s pilot of BrightDrop electric vans highlights GM’s expanding presence in green logistics, strategic partnerships, and strong dividend growth potential.
